                <head>134. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d134fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, <gloss target="#t_NSC_1">NSC</gloss> Institutional Files
                        (H–Files), Box 107. Top Secret. The meeting took place in the White House
                        Situation Room. <persName corresp="#p_CJ_1">Carter</persName> wrote “Zbig,
